<br>
Plane of Innovation Trains can be rather vicious at times, occasionally taking out 2-3 groups along the way when someone tries to make a run from a long way off. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Most of the time it just results in wasted mana and an inconvenience.<br>
<br>
As nasty as the zone-in can be sometimes, the behavior of the Clerics passing through has been superb. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   The graveyard usually has a few bodies on it at any time of day, but I don't think many aren't getting 96% rezzes.  Thank you Priests and Priestesses of Norrath for your generosity and aid to our fallen comrades! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
