&quot;/shout train from left&quot; can allow those at zone-in to move just up the right path (or vice versa) and avoid the nasties you couldn't handle.<br>
<br>
btw, Illusion Imp form gives indifferent faction to almost all the mobs in PoI (with a few exceptions), and can help you explore/scout/move.<br>
